name: Mapping R
body:
### Welcome to Mapping with R
A workshop for mapping with R.
---
Download the data for this workshop using the tar.gz or .zip folders above. Workshop instructions are available as a .pdf in the downloaded files, or [as a webpage](http://clarkdatalabs.github.io/mapping_R/workshop).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
